<!--pages/member/home/home.wxml-->

<view class="section">
  <view class="section__title">普通选择器</view>
  <picker bindchange="bindPickerChange" value="{{index}}" range="{{array}}" disabled="{{ship}}">
    <view class="picker">

      <view class='cu-custom'>
        <view class="cu-bar fixed" style="height:{{CustomBar}}px;padding-top:{{StatusBar}}px;">
          <navigator class='action' open-type="navigateBack" delta="1" hover-class="none">
            <text class='cuIcon-back text-white'></text>
            <text class='text-white'></text>
          </navigator>
          <view class='content' style='top:{{StatusBar}}px;'></view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <swiper class="screen-swiper square-dot" indicator-dots="true" circular="true" autoplay="true" interval="5000" duration="500">
        <swiper-item wx:for="{{album}}" wx:key="{{index}}" bindtap="ViewImage" data-url="{{album[index]}}">
          <image class='response' src="{{item}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        </swiper-item>
      </swiper>
      <view class='padding'>

        <view class="margin-bottom-xl">
          <view class='margin-bottom-xs flex align-center'>
            <text class="text-cut margin-right-sm text-black text-bold text-df">马达</text>
            <text class="cu-tag round bg-orange sm"><text class='cuIcon-safe lg text-white text-xs'></text> 已认证</text>
          </view>
          <view class='text-gray text-sm'>
            <text class='cuIcon-female text-pink'></text>
            <text>  94年・水瓶座・160CM・深大 本科・教师</text>
          </view>
          <view class='text-gray text-sm'>
            <text><text class="cuIcon-locationfill"></text> 现居深圳・广东人</text>
          </view>
          <view class='margin-top-sm flex justify-start align-center'>
            <!-- <view class='text-gray'>来历：</view> -->
            <scroll-view scroll-x>
              <view class="source-group padding-lr-xs flex">
                <view class="source-item flex">
                  <view class='source-user flex flex-direction justify-center align-center'>
                    <view class="cu-avatar round" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10001.jpg);"></view>
                    <view class='text-gray text-xs'>马达</view>
                  </view>
                  <view class='source-connection'>
                    <view class='source-line'></view>
                    <text class="cu-tag round bg-green sm">父亲</text>
                  </view>
                </view>
                <view class="source-item flex">
                  <view class='source-user flex flex-direction justify-center align-center'>
                    <view class="cu-avatar round" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10002.jpg);"></view>
                    <view class='text-gray text-xs'>大强</view>
                  </view>
                  <view class='source-connection'>
                    <view class='source-line'></view>
                    <text class="cu-tag round bg-green sm">朋友</text>
                  </view>
                </view>
                <view class="source-item flex">
                  <view class='source-user flex flex-direction justify-center align-center'>
                    <view class="cu-avatar round" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10003.jpg);"></view>
                    <view class='text-gray text-xs'>谢广坤</view>
                  </view>
                  <view class='source-connection'>
                    <view class='source-line'></view>
                    <text class="cu-tag round bg-green sm">儿子</text>
                  </view>
                </view>
                <view class="source-item flex">
                  <view class='source-user flex flex-direction justify-center align-center'>
                    <view class="cu-avatar round" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10004.jpg);"></view>
                    <view class='text-gray text-xs'>我</view>
                  </view>
                </view>
              </view>
            </scroll-view>

          </view>

          <!-- <scroll-view scroll-x class=" padding response cu-steps steps-bottom" scroll-into-view="scroll-{{scroll}}" scroll-with-animation>
            <view class="cu-item {{index>scroll?'':'text-blue'}} padding-lr-xl" wx:for="{{10}}" wx:key id="scroll-{{index}}">
            Level {{index + 1}} <text class="num" data-index="{{index + 1}}"></text>
            </view>    </scroll-view> -->


        </view>
        <view class="section">
          <view class="section-title">
            <text class="cuIcon-titles text-pink"></text>
            <text class="text-df">自我描述</text>
          </view>
          <view class="section-content margin-top-sm">
            性格比较直爽，基本就是会哈哈大笑的那种，晚上很爱说，但还是期待别人能主动哈哈哈，不爱说服别人，比较随缘，信佛。一个内心比较细腻的水瓶座，期待一个可以让我撒娇的人。
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="section margin-top-xl">
          <view class="section-title">
            <text class="cuIcon-titles text-pink"></text>
            <text class="text-df">家庭背景</text>
          </view>
          <view class="section-content margin-top-sm">
            从小和妈妈一起长大，妈妈很开明开朗独立，对我影响很深，同时某方面还是会传统保守些，本人很看重家庭观念，自以为是比较孝顺妈妈的，希望遇到的他也能珍惜家人。
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="section margin-top-xl">
          <view class="section-title">
            <text class="cuIcon-titles text-pink"></text>
            <text class="text-df">兴趣爱好</text>
          </view>
          <view class="section-content margin-top-sm">
            <text>喜欢尝试新东西，喜欢练街舞，爱狗狗，寒暑假会想出去走走，偶尔爱在家宅一天。会英语法语和交传。
            </text>
            <view class='margin-top flex flex-direction justify-between'>
              <image src='cloud://test-t2od1.7465-test-t2od1/WechatIMG10.jpeg' mode='widthFix'></image>
              <image src='cloud://test-t2od1.7465-test-t2od1/WechatIMG11.jpeg' mode='widthFix'></image>
              <image src='cloud://test-t2od1.7465-test-t2od1/WechatIMG12.jpeg' mode='widthFix'></image>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="section margin-top-xl">
          <view class="section-title">
            <text class="cuIcon-titles text-pink"></text>
            <text class="text-df">爱情观</text>
          </view>
          <view class="section-content margin-top-sm">
            <text>满心期待爱，也坦然接受爱永不到来，爱情，不过是锦上添花，所以绝不将就
            </text>
          </view>
        </view>


        <view class="section margin-top-xl">
          <view class="section-title">
            <text class="cuIcon-titles text-pink"></text>
            <text class="text-df">理想的另一半</text>
          </view>
          <view class="section-content margin-top-sm">
            <text>希望他具有有趣的灵魂，可以在一起吧生活活得平凡又好玩，最好是有梗，可以跟我一起哈哈大笑，能积极进取，有事业心的男人比较有魅力，不喜欢一潭死水整天沉迷游戏，希望他偶尔能跟我多出去走走，享受阳光雨露，同时也有点兴趣爱好，打球什么的都可以。</text>
          </view>
        </view>


        <view class="section margin-top-xl">
          <view class="section-title">
            <text class="cuIcon-titles text-pink"></text>
            <text class="text-df">我为什么单身？</text>
          </view>
          <view class="section-content margin-top-sm">
          <text>工作环境单纯，每天都是接触小孩子，比较少接触外面的人，宁缺毋滥，不想将就</text>
          </view>
        </view>


        <view class="section margin-top-xl">
          <view class="section-title">
            <text class="cuIcon-titles text-pink"></text>
            <text class="text-df">如果遇到对的人，我期待什么样的生活？</text>
          </view>
          <view class="section-content margin-top-sm">
          <text>共同扶持，一起进步，一起相信未来可期吧吧吧吧，如果可以遇到对的人，希望他能不轻易就放弃，因为我愿意认真对待。</text>
          </view>
        </view>

      </view>

      <view wx:if="{{source == 'meet'}}" class="btn-group cu-bar tabbar foot">
        <button bindtap="bindLike" class="cu-btn bg-red round">感兴趣</button>
        <button open-type="share" class="cu-btn bg-green round">推荐给好友</button>
      </view>

      <view class="cu-tabbar-height"></view>

      <!-- 当前选择：{{array[index]}} -->
    </view>
  </picker>
</view>